OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry. Then the rest of the
OL,7,Fnight will remain dry across all parts
OL,8,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,9,Fclear periods.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FAfter a dry morning rain
OL,12,Fwill spread southeast during the
OL,13,Fafternoon. Mild in the morning but
OL,14,Fturning colder during the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,17,Ffor most of Thursday but patchy rain
OL,18,Fspreading east later. Unsettled with
OL,19,Fshowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,20,FFriday and Saturday.
